<p begin="00:00:06.273" end="00:00:06.840" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(CHEERS AND APPLAUSE).</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:06.840" end="00:00:07.541" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: WELCOME BACK.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:07.541" end="00:00:11.345" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MY GUEST TONIGHT, HIS NEW FAME </span><span style="block">IS CALLED "CHASING MAVERICKS."</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:11.345" end="00:00:12.813" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; I WANT TO RIDE THAT WAVE.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:12.813" end="00:00:13.947" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I WANT TO THAT I CAN THAT DROP.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:13.947" end="00:00:15.449" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; IT'S NOT GONNA HAPPEN.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:15.449" end="00:00:16.917" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; WHY NOT?</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:16.917" end="00:00:21.488" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; BECAUSE UNTRAINED BOYS DON'T </span><span style="block">STEP IN THE RING WITH MIKE </span><span style="block">TYSON, THAT'S WHY.</span></p>


<p begin="00:00:21.488" end="00:00:22.856" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; I CAN HANDLE IT!</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:22.856" end="00:00:25.659" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; YOU DON'T JUST DO IT.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:25.659" end="00:00:28.428" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BUDDY, I'VE BEEN SURFING THAT </span><span style="block">BREAK FOR 20 YEARS.</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:28.428" end="00:00:32.533" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA HOW MUCH </span><span style="block">STRENGTH AND KNOW HOW YOU NEED </span><span style="block">TO SURVIVE A BREAK LIKE THAT?</span></p>


<p begin="00:00:32.533" end="00:00:34.835" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; I'M GETTING STRONGER BY THE </span><span style="block">DAY.</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:34.835" end="00:00:36.270" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I'LL HOLD MY OWN.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:36.270" end="00:00:39.840" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; STRONGER BY THE DAY, HUH?</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:39.840" end="00:00:42.843" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">OKAY, GAVE ME YOUR HAND.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:42.843" end="00:00:44.878" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">NOW RESIST ME.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:44.878" end="00:00:45.312" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">OKAY?</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:45.312" end="00:00:47.548" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">NO, YOU'RE NOT --</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:47.548" end="00:00:49.583" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: OH, I'M SORRY.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:49.583" end="00:00:52.719" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(LAUGHTER) </span><span style="block">PLEASE WELCOME GERARD BUTLER!</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:52.719" end="00:01:03.730" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(CHEERS AND APPLAUSE)</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:03.730" end="00:01:05.499" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: NICE TO SEE YOU.</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:05.499" end="00:01:16.109" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(CHEERS AND APPLAUSE) </span><span style="block">I GUESS MY FIRST THING I'M GOING </span><span style="block">SAY TO YOU IS THIS "GRAB MY </span><span style="block">HAND." </span><span style="block">(LAUGHTER)</span></p>




<p begin="00:01:16.109" end="00:01:17.978" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">RESIST ME, BUTLER!</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:17.978" end="00:01:21.181" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THOSE AREN'T HANDS THEY'RE LIKE </span><span style="block">(BLEEP)ING MEAT HOOKS, JESUS!</span></p>

<p begin="00:01:21.181" end="00:01:23.150" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">WHAT'S HAPPENING?</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:23.150" end="00:01:26.887" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; NOTHING, MAN, JUST -- I JUST </span><span style="block">REALIZED HOW MUCH I MISSED MY </span><span style="block">HAIR.</span></p>


<p begin="00:01:26.887" end="00:01:27.521" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I MEAN IT'S --</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:27.521" end="00:01:28.488" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: OH, IS THAT TRUE.</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:28.488" end="00:01:31.225" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; YEAH, IT DOESN'T REALLY LOOK </span><span style="block">LIKE IT WAS, MY HAIR.</span></p>

<p begin="00:01:31.225" end="00:01:38.966" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: YOU LIKE IT MORE </span><span style="block">FLOWING, A LITTLE MORE </span><span style="block">"BRAVEHEARTY." </span><span style="block">AS MUCH -T AS IT LOOKED BLEACHED</span></p>



<p begin="00:01:38.966" end="00:01:41.001" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">AS HELL BUT IT WAS A FUN CUT.</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:41.001" end="00:01:42.002" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon:</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:42.002" end="00:01:43.303" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: LET ME ASK YOU THIS.</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:43.303" end="00:01:47.341" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">DID YOU DO THE THINGS YOU WANTED </span><span style="block">TO DO WITH YOUR HAIR WHEN IT WAS </span><span style="block">THAT LONG OR NO?</span></p>


<p begin="00:01:47.341" end="00:01:51.111" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">DID YOU GET A CONVERTIBLE AND </span><span style="block">DRIVE LIKE THIS?</span></p>

